                "actions": {
                    "value": 2
                },
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The spiral centurion hurls one of its blades with an angled spin to ensure a swooping flight path. The blade deals [[/r 6d6 #slashing]]{6d6 slashing damage} to each creature in a 40-foot line (<span data-pf2-check=\"reflex\" data-pf2-dc=\"30\" data-pf2-traits=\"damaging-effect\" data-pf2-label=\"Hurl Blade DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">basic Reflex</span> save).</p>\n<p>At the start of the spiral centurion's next turn, the blade swoops around and returns along the same flight path, again dealing [[/r 6d6 #slashing]]{6d6 slashing damage} (<span data-pf2-check=\"reflex\" data-pf2-dc=\"30\" data-pf2-traits=\"damaging-effect\" data-pf2-label=\"Hurl Blade DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">basic Reflex</span> save) to each creature along the same line.</p>"
